summary: This document is a criminal history inquiry response from the New York State Division of Criminal Justice Services regarding NYSID Number 10106%2021. It indicates no criminal history found in NYS records for the individual, but cautions that identification is not based on fingerprint comparison and that the FBI may have records.

persons.name: Michael C. Green
persons.role: Executive Deputy Commissioner of the NYS Division of Criminal Justice Services
persons.context: Listed as the executive deputy commissioner of the agency issuing the criminal history inquiry response.

keyFacts: The document is a criminal history inquiry response from the New York State Division of Criminal Justice Services dated October 6, 2021.
No criminal history or releasable criminal history information was found in NYS records for the inquired NYSID number.
The identification is cautioned as not being based on fingerprint comparison.
The response notes that the FBI may have a record even if NYS does not, and directs inquiries to the FBI.
The document includes a warning about unauthorized release of information being prohibited by federal law (Title 42 USC 3789g(b)).
